* Drone strikes being conducted by the [[Central Intelligence Agency|CIA]]
'''[[Military intervention against ISIL|International campaign against ISIL (2014–present)]]:'''
* Ongoing insurgency
* [[Operation Inherent Resolve]]: U.S.-led Coalition airstrikes on ISIL positions in [[American-led intervention in Iraq (2014–present)|Iraq]], [[American-led intervention in Syria|Syria]], [[2015 Egyptian military intervention in Libya|Egyptian airstrikes in Libya]], and [[Boko Haram insurgency|West African airstrikes in Nigeria]]
* Multinational humanitarian effort
* Arming and support for local ground forces
* [[ISIL beheading incidents|ISIL beheadings]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.thedailybeast.com/articles/2014/08/21/obama-readies-for-war-on-isis.html|title=Obama vs ISIS: This time it's personal|date=22 August 2014|accessdate=9 September 2014|website=The Daily Beast}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2014/08/23/world/middleeast/obama-adviser-says-military-action-possible-against-isis.html|title=U.S. weighs direct military action against ISIS in Syria|date=22 August 2014|accessdate=9 September 2014|work=The New York Times|first1=Peter|last1=Baker|first2=Michael D.|last2=Shear}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-europe-29360788|title=French hostage beheading: France to boost Syria rebels|work=BBC News|accessdate=28 September 2014|date=25 September 2014}}</ref><ref name="The Huffington Post">{{cite news|url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2014/12/01/william-henderson-oil-worker-killed_n_6246202.html|title=Islamic State Allies In Egypt Say They Killed American Oil Worker William Henderson|work=The Huffington Post|accessdate=6 December 2014|date=1 December 2014}}</ref><ref name=BBCKassig1>{{cite news|title=Islamic State Kassig murder: Western jihadists probed|url=https://www.bbc.com/news/world-middle-east-30080874|accessdate=17 November 2014|work=BBC.com|date=17 November 2014}}</ref><ref>[http://america.aljazeera.com/articles/2015/2/10/kayler-mueller-american-isil-hostage-is-dead.html "Kayla Mueller, American ISIL hostage, is dead"], ''[[Al Jazeera America]],'' 10 February 2015</ref><ref name="Egypt retaliates for the killings of 21 Egyptians">{{cite news|url=https://www.bbc.com/news/world-middle-east-31483631|agency=BBC News|title=Egypt 'bombs IS in Libya' after beheadings video|date=16 February 2015|accessdate=16 February 2015}}</ref>
